  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GeoWaveDedupeMapper

    public abstract class GeoWaveWritableOutputMapper<KEYIN,VALUEIN>
extends org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce.Mapper<KEYIN,VALUEIN,GeoWaveInputKey,org.apache.hadoop.io.ObjectWritable>
    This abstract class can be extended by GeoWave analytics. It handles the conversion of native GeoWave objects into objects that are writable. It is a mapper that converts to writable objects for the output. This conversion will only work if the data adapter implements HadoopDataAdapter.
